# ============================================
# DEPLOYMENT INSTRUCTIONS:
# ============================================
# 1. Get your database password from Supabase Dashboard
# 2. Update DB_PASSWORD above
# 3. Generate a strong JWT_SECRET (use: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))")
# 4. Deploy backend to Railway/Render
# 5. Deploy frontend to Vercel/Netlify
# 6. Update CORS_ORIGIN with your actual frontend URL
# 7. Add all these variables to your hosting platform (Railway/Render)
